1. Activate the mod_global_chat Module from Zotonic Admin.

2. In the base template as the following line
   {% all include "_application_head.tpl" %}

3. Add the following line in the template where you want to show the chat button
   {% include "_global_chat_button.tpl" %} 

4. You will be now able to use the chat. 

Note: Message are not saved if the page refreshed or the chat dialog is closed messages will be lost.
